channel.title: Dense - E/E (James Lucien) [House]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/dense-auxy-mix
This is the other remaining track as E/E that has currently been posted. This is an Auxy remix of the original song, which was done painstakingly in pure Garageband. This mix is a hybrid blend to get the strings in there as well. It's not perfect, but it's certainly kicking especially as my second ever real House track.
[(Here is the original mix, if you're so inclined. It isn't as good as the Auxy mix, had a lot of issues and such)](https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/dense)
![dense|500x500](upload://cdkBfXSGVNRbjXjRsi5O0JzLgad.jpg)

item.title: Dense - E/E (James Lucien) [House]
item.dc:creator: therealejoc
item.description:
Ahhh the strings are so nice. Really nice house track. Maybe make the kicks slight ly more audible because everything is loud and without headphones I cant really hear them. That’s just a minor hung though because you can still sense where they are as a whole. Love this song though. Very well done.
